Gate (Erc20 DAI Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard DAI "Dai")
Gate (Erc20 REP Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard REP "Augur")
Gate (Erc20 USDC Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard USDC "USD Coin" 6)

-- Now deploy our vTokens
Gate (VToken cZRX Address) (VToken Deploy VErc20 cZRX "Test 0x ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 ZRX Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (VToken cBAT Address) (VToken Deploy VErc20 cBAT "Test Basic Attention Token ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 BAT Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (VToken cDAI Address) (VToken Deploy VErc20 cDAI "Test Dai ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 DAI Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (VToken cREP Address) (VToken Deploy VErc20 cREP "Test Augur ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 REP Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
